Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}只要知道了方法就很簡單了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}這樣的話我就不會輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}你就是衝著這東西來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我可不想欠你人情 這樣就還清了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}我們回去吧 小圓
